item.title: I made a (free to read & share) novel
item.description: Quick note: I’ll probably delete this post at some point. It’s more of me using my RSS to share something that I’ve been working on and less of a real blog post. Just thought I would mention so it doesn’t look like I’m retracting anything and to give a heads up in case you were planning on bookmarking it. Anyway, I’ve been working on a novel aptly named “An Untitled Novel”.
